<h2>Confirm Your Account</h2>
<p><strong>Welcome <%= @user.email_address %>!</strong></p>
<p>Thank you for signing up with Piegon. We're excited to have you on board!</p>
<p>Please confirm your account by clicking the button below:</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0;">
  <%= link_to "Confirm My Account", @confirmation_url, class: "btn" %>
</div>

<p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
<p style="word-break: break-all; font-family: monospace; background-color: #f5f5f5; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #cccccc;"><%= @confirmation_url %></p>